=== 開發與製作背景 ===
{{link-en|吉兒·索洛威|Jill Soloway}}為[[亞馬遜公司|亞馬遜公司]]開創了《透明家庭》試播集，並於2014年2月6日提供免費串流與下載，成為{{link-en|亞馬遜工作室|Amazon Studios#2nd pilot season (February 6, 2014)|亞馬遜第二試播環}}獲系列預訂的其中一部電視劇。<ref name=HitFix-Trans-2014>{{cite news|last1=Fienberg|first1=Daniel|title=Interview: 'Transparent' creator Jill Soloway discusses her Amazon pilot|url=http://www.hitfix.com/the-fien-print/interview-transparent-creator-jill-soloway-discusses-her-amazon-pilot|accessdate=2014-08-31|work=[[HitFix|HitFix]]|date=2014-02-15}}</ref><ref name=Vuture-Transparent-2014>{{cite news|last1=Lyons|first1=Margaret|title=Talking to Jill Soloway About Her Wonderful Amazon Pilot, Transparent|url=http://www.vulture.com/2014/02/jill-soloway-on-her-amazon-pilot-transparent.html|accessdate=2014-08-31|work=[[紐約_(雜誌)|Vulture]]|date=2014-02-13}}</ref>索洛威表示本劇靈感是來自於其跨性別父親，<ref>{{cite news |last= Wilson|first= Stacey|date= 2014-12-17|title= 'Transparent' Boss Reveals the Moment She Decided to Make a Show About a Transgender Parent|url= http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/transparent-boss-reveals-moment-she-758426|newspaper= [[荷里活報道|好萊塢報導]]|location= |accessdate= 2014-12-25}}</ref>並想藉由本劇來探討[[性別認同|性別認同]]的議題，有意想描寫一個遍體鱗傷的父親如何慢慢轉變成一個如花般的女人，同時她在創造莫拉／莫特一角時，是想像{{link-en|傑弗瑞·坦伯|Jeffrey Tambor}}來飾演此角色。<ref name=Variety-Trans-2014 />

製作期間，索洛威宣布了一項重大變革，那就是跨性別者將會比非跨性別者更優先錄用。<ref name=NYTimes-Transparent-2014>{{cite news|last1=Brodesser-Akner|first1=Taffy|title=Can Jill Soloway Do Justice to the Trans Movement?|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/08/31/magazine/can-jill-soloway-do-justice-to-the-trans-movement.html?Src=longreads&_r=0|accessdate=2014-08-31|work=[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]|date=2014-08-29}}</ref>{{as of|2014年8月}}，本劇已有80位跨性別者於本劇工作，其中包含2名跨性別者顧問。<ref name=NYTimes-Transparent-2014 />2014年，{{link-en|Our Lady J|Our Lady J}}成為首位為本劇撰寫劇本的公開跨性別者。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.advocate.com/arts-entertainment/television/2014/12/04/transparent-creator-shows-first-trans-writer|title='Transparent' Creator on Show's First Trans Writer|author=Dawn Ennis|work=Advocate.com}}</ref>本劇廁所皆為無性別廁所。<ref name=Vulture-Girls/Trans-2014>{{cite news|last1=Martin|first1=Denise|title=Gaby Hoffmann on Girls, Growing Up in ’80s New York, and Her Amazon Show Transparent|url=http://www.vulture.com/2014/09/gaby-hoffmann-on-her-amazon-show-transparent.html|accessdate=2014-09-03|work=Vulture|publisher=[[紐約_(雜誌)|紐約雜誌]]|date=2014-09-02}}</ref>

2013年10月，本劇獲得試播集預訂，<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2013/10/03/prime-instant-video-greenlights-three-new-pilots-241013/20131003amazon01/|title=Prime Instant Video Greenlights Three New Pilots|work=[[富頓評論家|富頓評論家]]|date=2013-10-03|accessdate=2017-11-19}}</ref>並在2014年3月獲得系列預訂。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2014/03/31/six-more-amazon-original-pilots-receive-greenlight-for-full-seasons-the-after-bosch-gortimer-gibbons-life-on-normal-street-mozart-in-the-jungle-transparent-and-wishenpoof-897103/20140331amazon02/|title=Six More Amazon Original Pilots Receive Greenlight for Full Seasons: "The After," "Bosch," "Gortimer Gibbon's Life on Normal Street," "Mozart in the Jungle," "Transparent" and "Wishenpoof!"|work=富頓評論家|date=2014-03-31|accessdate=2017-11-19}}</ref>原始試播集於2014年2月釋出，在獲得全季預訂後，部分場景重新拍攝，同時也更替了一些演員，<ref>{{cite news|title="Transparent" Original pilot|url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt3976338/combined|accessdate=2015-01-02|location=[[互聯網電影數據庫|IMDb]]|archive-date=2020-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200603071139/https://www.imdb.com/title/tt3976338/reference|dead-url=no}}</ref>並於2014年9月底釋出第一季所有集數。<ref name=Variety-Trans-TCAs-2014>{{cite news|last1=Yeo|first1=Debra|title=Amazon’s ‘Transparent’ Season 1 to Debut Late September, ‘Bosch’ Premiering Early 2015|url=http://variety.com/2014/digital/news/amazon-transparent-full-season-premiere-bosch-2015-1201261698/|accessdate=2014-08-31|work=綜藝雜誌|date=2014-07-12}}</ref>於[[加拿大|加拿大]]，本劇由{{link-en|Shomi|Shomi}}於2015年1月23日首播。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Katz|first1=Jessie|title=TV series Transparent coming to Shomi|url=http://www.thestar.com/entertainment/television/2015/01/12/tv_series_transparent_coming_to_shomi.html|accessdate=2015-01-12|work=[[多倫多明星日報|多倫多明星日報]]|date=2015-01-12}}</ref>

2014年10月9日，宣布續訂第2季。<ref name=HitFix-S2Renewal-2014>{{cite news|last1=Sepinwall|first1=Alan|title=Amazon Renews 'Transparent' For Season 2|url=http://www.hitfix.com/whats-alan-watching/amazon-renews-transparent-for-season-2
|accessdate=2014-10-10|work=[[HitFix|HitFix]]|date=2014-10-09}}</ref>2015年7月1日，宣布續訂第3季。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2015/06/transparent-renewed-season-3-amazon-jill-soloway-overall-deal-1201455444/ |title=‘Transparent’ Renewed For Season 3 By Amazon; Creator Jill Soloway Inks Overall Deal |publisher=Deadline.com |first=Nellie |last=Andreeva |date=2015-06-25 |accessdate=2015-07-01}}</ref>2016年5月31日，在第3季首播前，亞馬遜提前續訂第4季。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2016/05/transparent-renewed-season-4-amazon-1201764671/ |title=‘Transparent’ Renewed For Season 4 By Amazon|publisher=Deadline.com|first=Denise|last=Petski|date=2016-05-31|accessdate=2016-05-31}}</ref>2017年8月24日，亞馬遜提前宣布續訂第5季。<ref name="Season 5">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2017/08/transparent-renewed-season-5-amazon-1202155348/|title=‘Transparent’ Renewed For Season 5 By Amazon|publisher=Deadline.com|first=Denise|last=Petski|date=2017-08-24|accessdate=2017-08-27}}</ref>

2017年9月11日，宣布由於索洛威將負責亞馬遜其他影集的製作，吉兒·戈登將加入本劇第5季執行製作陣容，接替索洛威擔任節目統籌。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2017/09/transparent-jill-gordon-showrunner-amazon-comedy-series-1202164858/|title=‘Transparent’: Jill Gordon Named Showrunner Of Amazon Comedy Series|publisher=Deadline.com|author=Nellie Andreeva|date=2017-09-11|accessdate=2017-09-11}}</ref>2018年5月7日，索洛威證實第5季為劇集的最終季。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tvline.com/2018/05/07/transparent-cancelled-season-6-amazon-jeffrey-tambor-leaving/|title=''Transparent'' Ending After Season 5 Without Jeffrey Tambor, Says Creator|publisher={{le|TVLine|TVLine}}|author=Matt Webb Mitovich|date=2018-05-07|accessdate=2018-05-07}}</ref>

