=== 選角 ===
{{link-en|傑弗瑞·坦伯|Jeffrey Tambor}}飾演跨性別父親，而{{link-en|蓋比·霍夫曼|Gaby Hoffmann}}、[[傑·杜普拉斯|傑·杜普拉斯]]與{{link-en|愛咪·蘭德克|Amy Landecker}}則飾演他的兒女們，而這一家人將一同歷經一場家庭與生活上轉變。<ref name=HReporter-Transparent-2014>{{cite news|last1=Goodman|first1=Tim|title=Amazon's New Crop of Pilots, Including Chris Carter's 'The After': TV Review|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/amazon-tv-pilots-reviewed-680925|accessdate=2014-08-31|work=好萊塢報導|date=2014-02-18}}</ref>傑弗瑞·坦伯也曾於1980年代的警匪電視劇《{{link-en|希爾街警網|Hill Street Blues}}》中飾演[[跨性別|跨性別者]]法官艾倫·旺秋（{{lang|en|Alan Wachtel}}）。<ref name=SpokesmanReview-HSB-1990->{{cite news|last1=Burlingame|first1=Jon|title='Wiseguy' uncorks a rousing season finale|url=http://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1314&dat=19900411&id=CvpPAAAAIBAJ&sjid=TwgEAAAAIBAJ&pg=2654,91770|accessdate=2014-10-04|work={{link-en|言論評論報|The Spokesman-Review}}|date=1990-04-11|archive-date=2020-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200603071139/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1314&dat=19900411&id=CvpPAAAAIBAJ&sjid=TwgEAAAAIBAJ&pg=2654,91770&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>索洛威在觀看蓋比·霍夫曼於[[路易·C·K|路易·C·K]]的影集《{{link-en|路易不容易|Louie (TV series)}}》中的演出後，才著手創造了莎拉一角。<ref name=HReporter-Trans-JillGabyDuos-2014>{{cite news|last1=Katz|first1=Jessie|title=Pret-a Reporter: Dynamic Duos: Jill Soloway and Gaby Hoffmann are Ready to Inhabit Your Brain|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/dynamic-duos-jill-soloway-gaby-687730|accessdate=2014-09-01|work=好萊塢報導|date=2014-03-11}}</ref>

2017年11月，亞馬遜證實坦伯的前助理凡·巴恩斯（{{lang|en|Van Barnes}}）控訴坦伯多次對她口出淫穢言論，並有不當的觸碰行為等，<ref name="Van Barnes">{{cite news|url=http://deadline.com/2017/11/jeffrey-tambor-sexual-harassment-claims-amazon-1202204220/|title=Jeffrey Tambor Being Investigated By Amazon On Sexual Harassment Claims; Actor “Adamantly” Denies Allegations|work=Deadline.com|author1=Dominic Patten|author2=Nellie Andreeva|date=2017-11-08|accessdate=2017-11-19|archive-date=2017-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171108202122/http://deadline.com/2017/11/jeffrey-tambor-sexual-harassment-claims-amazon-1202204220/|dead-url=no}}</ref>跨性別女星翠絲·利賽特（{{lang|en|Trace Lysette}}）亦隨後出面指控坦伯對她進行相關的性騷擾行為。<ref name="Trace Lysette">{{cite news|url=http://deadline.com/2017/11/jeffrey-tambor-sexual-harassment-claims-trace-lysette-transparent-actress-amazon-1202210145/|title=Jeffrey Tambor Accused By ‘Transparent’ Actress Of Sexual Harassment; Actor Admits “Flaws,” Says “Misinterpreted”|work=Deadline.com|author=Dominic Patten|date=2017-11-16|accessdate=2017-11-19|archive-date=2017-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171120085339/http://deadline.com/2017/11/jeffrey-tambor-sexual-harassment-claims-trace-lysette-transparent-actress-amazon-1202210145/|dead-url=no}}</ref>對此，亞馬遜展開了調查，而坦伯則嚴正地否認任何不當行為的指控，他認為自己「並非總是那麼好共事的人。我會不穩定且情緒暴躁，有時也會不知分寸而強烈地表達個人意見。但我不是個加害人－從來不是。」<ref name="Van Barnes"/><ref name="Trace Lysette"/>坦伯對於相關指控感到痛心，在性騷擾風波席捲好萊塢的政治氛圍下，輿論猜測坦伯可能會被節目開除，但坦伯最終選擇在19日主動辭演本劇。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://deadline.com/2017/11/jeffrey-tambor-leaving-transparent-sexual-harassment-allegations-amazon-jill-soloway-1202211711/|title=Jeffrey Tambor Exits ‘Transparent’ After Sexual Harassment Allegations|work=Deadline.com|author=Dominic Patten|date=2017-11-19|accessdate=2017-11-19|archive-date=2017-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171120022237/http://deadline.com/2017/11/jeffrey-tambor-leaving-transparent-sexual-harassment-allegations-amazon-jill-soloway-1202211711/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2018年2月15日，亞馬遜在經過數月的調查後，正式宣布坦伯將不會回歸第5季，雖然官方並未公布調查結果，但據傳官方認為坦伯的行為難辭其咎。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://deadline.com/2018/02/jeffrey-tambor-out-transparent-amazon-series-harassment-investigation-1202290473/|title=Jeffrey Tambor Officially Out At ‘Transparent’ After Harassment Claims|work=Deadline.com|author=Dominic Patten|date=2018-02-15|accessdate=2018-02-20}}</ref>對此，坦伯表明了自己對索洛威的失望，以及認為調查過程充滿缺陷與偏頗。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://deadline.com/2018/02/jeffrey-tambor-transparent-fired-response-jill-soloway-amazon-1202291033/|title=Jeffrey Tambor Lashes Out At Jill Soloway, “Flawed” Amazon Investigation After ‘Transparent’ Exit|work=Deadline.com|author=Dominic Patten|author2=Patrick Hipes|date=2018-02-15|accessdate=2018-02-20}}</ref>

== 評價 ==
[[File:Transparent_(26954545054).jpg|thumb]]]]
《透明家庭》獲得了廣大的好評。於[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]整合的評論中，第1季獲得了98%的新鮮度、8.83/10分（54位評論家），評論家共識：「就如電視史的變化般的個人轉變，《透明家庭》提升了節目的成熟度，並真誠的獻上一個人的人生旅程、疙瘩與所有。」<ref name=RottenTomatoes>{{cite web|title=Transparent: Season 1|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/transparent/s01/|publisher=[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]|accessdate=2014-09-27}}</ref>第2季獲得了97%的新鮮度、9.17/10分（36位評論家），評論家共識：「《透明家庭》第2季提升了其戲劇化，同時保留著能夠作為一部時裝影集最佳典範之一貫的辛酸與幽默。」<ref>{{cite web|title=Transparent: Season 2|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/transparent/s02/|publisher=爛番茄|accessdate=2016-07-14}}</ref>第3季獲得了100%的新鮮度、8.44/10分（31位評論家），評論家共識：「一如既往的獨特、深刻與憂愁，《透明家庭》對費佛曼家庭卓越的情感描寫，持續超越其他喜劇與劇情類影集。」<ref>{{cite web|title=Transparent: Season 3|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/transparent/s03/|publisher=爛番茄|accessdate=2016-07-14}}</ref>第4季獲得了89%的新鮮度、7.5/10分（18位評論家），評論家共識：「《透明家庭》第4季放棄了嚴謹的敘事規則，以引人入勝的沉重繼續探索節目具抱負的獨特主題。」<ref>{{cite web|title=Transparent: Season 4|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/transparent/s04/|publisher=爛番茄|accessdate=2018-04-14}}</ref>

於[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]整合的評論中，第1季獲得92分（滿分100分；29位評論家），屬極佳的讚譽。<ref name=Metacritic>{{cite web|title=Transparent - Season 1 Reviews|url=http://www.metacritic.com/tv/transparent|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2016-07-14}}</ref>第2季獲得了94分（滿分100分；28位評論家），屬極佳的讚譽。<ref>{{cite web|title=Transparent - Season 2 Reviews|url=http://www.metacritic.com/tv/transparent/season-2|publisher=Metacritic|accessdate=2016-07-14}}</ref>第3季獲得了90分（滿分100分；15位評論家），屬極佳的讚譽。<ref>{{cite web|title=Transparent - Season 3 Reviews|url=http://www.metacritic.com/tv/transparent/season-3|publisher=Metacritic|accessdate=2016-07-14}}</ref>第4季獲得了74分（滿分100分；10位評論家），屬普遍的好評。<ref>{{cite web|title=Transparent - Season 4 Reviews|url=http://www.metacritic.com/tv/transparent/season-4|publisher=Metacritic|accessdate=2018-04-14}}</ref>

